<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="no-longer-not-any-longer">no longer / not ... any longer</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>不再：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He didn't smoke any longer after the operation.
动过手术后他不再抽烟了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>No longer has she kept in touch with us since she went abroad for further education. 
自从出国留学后，她就不再和我们保持联系了。</p><footer>2011 上海</footer></div></div>